name: Cindy Miller
text: Quick delivery! Pizza was good, little on the greasy side but still good!! Loved the online ordering process... Nice and easy and made Exactly like I wanted it! Thank you!

name: Nicolas Reed
text: Fast, and very personable.  I've been here extensively and there's never been a thing messed up about my order.  They kind of need to sharpen their slicer or put some elbow grease into it.

name: Lewis Elder
text: Good pizza and customer service usually get to go but was clean the few times ate inside

name: Sam Ahring
text: All about service when it comes to delivery. Faster than most huts i have ordered from.

name: dillion JONES
text: NEED A NEW STAFF SLOW AND MIGHT NEED TO TAKE A ua
